  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ISnmpConfiguration
    A configuration to be applied to an Snmp Session.
    ISnmpConfigurationFactory
    Factory for the creation of ISnmpConfigurations.
    ISnmpNotificationOidLookup
    Class able to look up OID from a given DeviceEntityDescription.FieldDescription
    ISnmpSession
    A wrapper for an snmp4j SNMP session, providing functionality to identify the session device and walk the device's tree of managed objects.
    ISnmpSessionFactory
    Factory for creating and configuring ISnmpSessions.
    IVariableBindingHandler
    A handler of variable bindings returned by an SNMP input operation.
